description: As the Decepticons wage their war on Cybertron, a group of Mini-Cons rescues their captured friends and escapes the planet.
Millions of years after the Great War started, a trio of Earth kids finds a group of deactivated Mini-Cons.
Megatron and the Decepticons try to recapture the Street Action Team, but are stopped by the arrival of the Autobots.
As the Transformers battle on Earth, a group of Mini-Cons comes to the aid of the Autobots
Desperate for more power, Megatron captures the Air Defense Team and reworks them into the Star Saber.
Megatron attacks the Autobots with the Star Saber, but they are saved by the arrival of the Land Military Team.
Strange lights in the sky and crop circles coincide with a mass exodus of the Earthbound Mini-Cons.
The Earthbound Mini-Cons find themselves as unwilling guests of the ones who crashed on the Moon.

Features Include:
Oh Baby, No Baby!
